<item>
            <title>[LU-15576] Interop sanity test_823: Create count not set to max precreate</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15576</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/96c360e4-cbca-46b4-8a8e-0371f9a8f4b4&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/96c360e4-cbca-46b4-8a8e-0371f9a8f4b4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_823 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Create count not set to max precreate.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This test was added in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/39967&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/39967&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13941&quot; title=&quot;parallel-scale/run_rr_alloc: Restrict create_count to valid range&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-13941&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-13941&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; osp: Silently lower requested create_count to maximum&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; and should just be skipped in interop testing with MDS older than 2.14.56&lt;/p&gt;





&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity test_823 - Create count not set to max precreate.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
